entries.title_d: Find a New Supply Route. We will update your nav computer with new waypoints of possible secure supply routes. Follow them and keep your eye out for any enemy threats. When you complete this mission, return to V3-FX in Moenia for your next assignment.
entries.title: Naboo system: Find New Supply Route.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Command: < Mission redirect! An Alliance transport needs your immediate assistance! >
entries.quest_patrol_t: Find a new supply route for the Alliance
entries.quest_patrol_d: The Alliance is trying to establish a new transport route in the Naboo system, away from Imperial attention. Your mission is to patrol this route to make sure that it's safe before we send in transports.
entries.quest_patrol3_d: Fly to this location and ensure that the Naboo system supply route is safe to use.
entries.quest_patrol2_d: Continue your search of the Naboo system. Ensure that this second navigation point is clear of hostiles.
entries.quest_patrol1_d: Fly to this nav point and ensure that it is safe. Eliminate any hostiles that you encounter.
entries.quest_location_d: Scout an updated transport route in the Naboo system. Report to V3-FX for immediate relay to Alliance HQ.
